basicInfo.name: Teo
basicInfo.flavor: The only thing known for certain about Teo is that he is a member of the Night Crows.

Normal Attack.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 100% of Physical Attack 1 time(s).
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 130% of Physical Attack.

Skill 1.name: Talon Strike
Skill 1.desc:
All Enemies
 - Deals Piercing damage equal to 130% of Physical Attack 1 time(s). [Additional 30% Crit Rate]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 170% of Physical Attack.
超越6段階達成効果
 - Increases Effect: Crit Rate to 100%.

Skill 2.name: Corvus Eclipse
Skill 2.desc:
All Enemies
 - Deals damage equal to 65% of Physical Attack 2 time(s). [Additional 30% Crit Rate]
 - 100% chance to inflict Buff Duration Reduction. [Reduced by: 2 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 85% of Physical Attack.
超越6段階達成効果
 - Increases Effect: Crit Rate to 100%.

Passive.name: Crow's Eyes
Passive.desc:
Self
 - Grants All Damage Nullification. [Ends After: Taking 3 Hit(s)]
 - Revives with Immortality upon falling in battle. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)] [Once per Battle]
 - Grants Physical Attack Boost upon gaining Immortality. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Adds Effect: 39% Physical Attack Boost upon triggering Immortality. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
超越2段階達成効果
 - Adds Effect: Skill Cooldown Reset upon gaining Immortality.
